load: wgpu::LoadOp::Clear(wgpu::Color {
    r: srgb_to_linear(bg[0]),
    g: srgb_to_linear(bg[1]),
    b: srgb_to_linear(bg[2]),
    a: bg[3] as f64,
}),
```

